# REQUIRED. ≤64 chars, lowercase letters/numbers/hyphens only.
# Prefer gerund form: "processing-pdfs", "summarizing-files", "reviewing-diffs".
# Must NOT contain "anthropic" or "claude".
name: doing-something

# REQUIRED. ≤1024 chars. Third person ("Extracts X…", not "I can…" or "You can…").
# Include BOTH what the skill does AND when to use it. The description is the
# trigger mechanism — see WRITING-DESCRIPTIONS.md (repo root) for how to write one.
description: One sentence on what this skill does. Use when <specific trigger conditions>.

# OPTIONAL (Claude Code only). Set true for skills with side effects you want
# to invoke manually with /skill-name rather than have Claude auto-fire.
# disable-model-invocation: true

# OPTIONAL. Pre-approve tools the skill uses, so Claude doesn't need to ask.
# allowed-tools: Read Grep Bash(git diff *)
